Package: EmStanS
Type: Package
Title: Embedded Standard Setting
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Daniel",
             family = "Lewis",
             role = c("aut", "cph")),
      person(given = "Sooyong",
             family = "Lee",
             email = "sooyongl09@utexas.edu",
             role = c("aut","cre")))
Maintainer: Sooyong Lee <sooyongl09@gmail.com>
Description: Provides functions for embedded standard setting, including data preparation,
    item-level summaries, cut score estimation, visualization, reporting, and simulation.
    The package implements embedded standard setting approaches such as ESS-Count and
    ESS-Weight to support the estimation of performance standards from item-achievement
    level descriptor alignments and empirical item information.
